name: All Nippon Airways 787-9 [JA877A] Wheelie Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
I've never seen a 787 keep its nose up as long as this one! Here we have All Nippon Airways' daily flight from Tokyo Haneda Airport to Vancouver, with one of their new 787-9s. The video includes ATC, touchdown, and some taxi footage. Enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
